OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FAn under-fire maternity and neonatal
OL,7,Funit at the John Radcliffe Hospital in
OL,8,FOxford has been heavily scrutinised in
OL,9,Fthe National Maternity & Neonatal
OL,10,FInvestigation.
OL,12,FThe report by Baroness Amos, the chair
OL,13,Fof the investigation and Master of
OL,14,FUniversity College Oxford, said
OL,15,Fstaffing pressures were leading to
OL,16,Fcompromised care, that in turn left
OL,17,Fwomen at risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FIt comes after a year of
OL,7,Finvestigations by ITV News Meridian
OL,8,Fwhich found that hundreds of families
OL,9,Fallege that poor care at the John
OL,10,FRadcliffe Hospital caused long term
OL,11,Fphysical and emotional harm.
OL,13,FWhile putting together the review,
OL,14,Fwhich was released on Tuesday 30 June,
OL,15,Fshe spoke to dozens of families who
OL,16,Fwere impacted and said underlying
OL,17,Ftheir stories is a "strong belief that
OL,18,Fharm was preventable."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FBaroness Amos said, "families
OL,7,Frepeatedly stressed to us the
OL,8,Ffollowing concerns: missed warning
OL,9,Fsigns, failure to act on known risks,
OL,10,Fand repetition of the same mistakes
OL,11,Ftime and time again, affecting
OL,12,Fdifferent families.
OL,14,F"Many linked this to a culture where
OL,15,Fdecisions were made without
OL,16,Fconsultation with families."
OL,18,FThe estate at the John Radcliffe was
OL,19,Fdeemed old and not fit for purpose,
OL,20,Fand as such, constrains how it copes
OL,21,Fwith high numbers of service users.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FFront life staff were emotional about
OL,7,Fthe pressures they were under and the
OL,8,Funsafe situations they felt they were
OL,9,Fworking in. The executive team
OL,10,Facknowledged that staff were under
OL,11,Fpressure, but it was deemed that they
OL,12,Fdid not consider that they fully
OL,13,Funderstood the cause of the distress
OL,14,Fstaff were experiencing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FOne theme running through the report
OL,7,Finclude issues around families not
OL,8,Fbeing listened to or taken seriously
OL,9,Fwhen raising concerns about their own
OL,10,Fhealth or their baby's condition. For
OL,11,Fexample clear warning signs, such as
OL,12,Fbleeding, reduced movements, or
OL,13,Fleaking waters.
OL,15,FTheir concerns were "not acted upon
OL,16,Funtil the situation became more
OL,17,Fserious" and "healthcare professionals
OL,18,Ftold them not to worry about symptoms,
OL,19,Fwithout any examinations being
OL,20,Fundertaken."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
