OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FThis is the all too familiar reality
OL,7,Ffor Joy & Daniel Kabiri whose baby son
OL,8,FElkan was stillborn in September 2025.
OL,10,FThe hospital admits there were missed
OL,11,Fopportunities throughout her
OL,12,Fpregnancy, with the Trust saying they
OL,13,Fare 'truly sorry' that 'poor
OL,14,Fcommunication' throughout her care
OL,15,Fcould have led to a different outcome.
OL,17,FJoy had previously undergone a LLETZ
OL,18,Fprocedure, which is a treatment to
OL,19,Fremove abnormal cells from the cervix,
OL,20,Fat the same hospital where she later
OL,21,Freceived her maternity care.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FDespite repeatedly informing multiple
OL,7,Fmembers of staff and midwives about
OL,8,Fthis history during her pregnancy, she
OL,9,Fsays it was never acted upon and key
OL,10,Fsymptoms were missed.
OL,12,F"They failed me, this is going to live
OL,13,Fwith me, live with us for the rest of
OL,14,Four lives," said Joy. Her husband,
OL,15,FDaniel, said that during the stillborn
OL,16,Fwhen the baby was being delivered,
OL,17,Fgetting contractions, she turned to
OL,18,Fhim and said "all this for nothing?"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FDaniel said "that this will forever
OL,7,Fstay with me," after trying to get
OL,8,Fpregnant for five years, "due to no
OL,9,Ffault of our ours, it was for nothing."
OL,11,FShe believes the system "let her down"
OL,12,Fbecause she felt "as it was my first
OL,13,Fpregnancy, they kept telling me that I
OL,14,Fhad no idea what dischages were normal
OL,15,Fand what they look like, I'm being
OL,16,Fworried...I was being dismissed every
OL,17,Fsingle time I went in."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
