PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FAs a Black family, they are also
OL,7,Fcommitted to raising awareness of
OL,8,Fdisparities in maternal and neonatal
OL,9,Foutcomes among Black and Asian
OL,10,Fcommunities.
OL,12,F"We know the risks are higher," Joy
OL,13,Fadded. "We want to start conversations
OL,14,Fand push for change within our
OL,15,Fcommunities and beyond."
OL,17,FBaroness Amos' report highlighted that
OL,18,Fracism and discrimination are
OL,19,F"embedded throughout the maternity and
OL,20,Fneonatal system."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@_O]uD@HOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/24
