PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FThey are being supported by Fletchers
OL,7,FSolicitors with a legal case against
OL,8,Fthe Trust, and meanwhile the couple
OL,9,Fhave launched a charity in Elkan's
OL,10,Fmemory.
OL,12,FSimon Crowther, Interim Chief
OL,13,FExecutive Officer, of Oxford
OL,14,FUniversity Hospitals Trust said: "In
OL,15,Fresponse to the investigation
OL,16,Ffindings, we have delivered additional
OL,17,Ftraining and guidance to help ensure
OL,18,Fmaternity staff are able to identify
OL,19,Fand manage similar risk factors during
OL,20,Fpregnancy."
OL,26,@vD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/24
