PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FAlmost 800 families have come forward
OL,7,Fto say they have experienced harm at
OL,8,Fthe John Radcliffe Hospital, one of
OL,9,Fthem is Angel-Kay Mason.
OL,11,FShe says her repeated warnings about
OL,12,Fher pregnancy were dismissed by staff,
OL,13,Fbefore her daughter Aria was delivered
OL,14,Fat 26 weeks and suffered life-changing
OL,15,Fcomplications.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FAngel-Kay Mason believes an
OL,7,Fundiagnosed infection contributed to
OL,8,FAria's disabilities, including
OL,9,Fcerebral palsy. Her medical notes
OL,10,Fstated her amniotic fluid was green
OL,11,Fand her uterus was warm which she has
OL,12,Fbeen told are signs of an infection.
OL,14,FThey say routine scans showed Aria was
OL,15,Fhealthy and believe the infection
OL,16,Fduring pregnancy led to their
OL,17,Fdaughter's health issues.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,F"Since day one of being pregnant, to
OL,7,Fthis day, they just did not listen,"
OL,8,Fsaid husband Marley. "They always
OL,9,Fthink they know better. And that is
OL,10,Fwhy my wife was so ill. And that is
OL,11,Fwhy my daughter is so ill and has so
OL,12,Fmany complications."
OL,14,FAngel-Kay is unimpressed with the
OL,15,Ffindings by Baroness Amos, saying "I
OL,16,Fthink that it was supposed to be a
OL,17,Ffamily centred report, there's five
OL,18,Fpages based on stuff that families
OL,19,Fhave said, there are eight pages based
OL,20,Foff of just what staff have told them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,F"I sat in the meeting with Baroness
OL,7,FAmos, I heard the testimonies of other
OL,8,Fpeople...the things she has chosen to
OL,9,Freport, doesn't do it any justice."
OL,11,FThe pair say they were disappointed to
OL,12,Fsee that disabilities weren't
OL,13,Fmentioned and have renewed calls for a
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry into the John Radcliffe
OL,15,FHospital for more accountability.
OL,17,FThey, like Joy & Daniel, are in the
OL,18,Fprocess of pursuing legal action
OL,19,Fagainst the Trust.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
