FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FIn response to claims made by Angel-
OL,7,FKay, the Trust said:
OL,9,F"We recognise how distressing this
OL,10,Fexperience was for Angel-Kay, Marley
OL,11,Fand their family, and we are truly
OL,12,Fsorry for this. "Angel-Kay and Marley
OL,13,Fhave raised several concerns and we
OL,14,Fwould welcome the opportunity to talk
OL,15,Fwith them directly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,Fhis would allow us to understand their
OL,7,Fexperience in full, review the care
OL,8,Fprovided, answer any questions they
OL,9,Fmay have and ensure they receive the
OL,10,Fsupport that feels most helpful to
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"The Trust takes all feedback and
OL,14,Fconcerns extremely seriously and is
OL,15,Fcommitted to listening to families,
OL,16,Flearning from their experiences and
OL,17,Fcontinually improving care so every
OL,18,Ffamily feels heard and supported."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
