FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FThe concerns regarding the review is
OL,7,Fechoed by Founder of Families Failed
OL,8,Fby OUH Maternity Services, Rebecca
OL,9,FMatthews. She herself experience
OL,10,Ftraumatic maternity care in Oxford and
OL,11,Fsaid the "report doesn't reflect the
OL,12,Fexperiences we all bravely shared"
OL,13,Fafter they "thought we'd been listened
OL,14,Fto & finally heard" after meeting with
OL,15,FBaroness Amos to provide evidence
OL,16,Fabout stillbirths, brain injuries and
OL,17,Fbirth trauma.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,F"The report gives double the coverage
OL,7,Fto staff," said Matthews. "In the main
OL,8,Freport the word 'caesarean' appears 11
OL,9,Ftimes yet families shared their
OL,10,Fexperiences of begging for caesareans
OL,11,Fand being denied planned caesareans
OL,12,Fand having to see psychiatrists to be
OL,13,Fable to access them.
OL,15,F"We feel like our voices have been
OL,16,Fwritten out of the investigation."
OL,26,@xD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G18/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FThe group has criticised the focus on
OL,7,Festates and staffing, saying the use
OL,8,Fof a descriptive analysis using AI
OL,9,F"might explain why the report focuses
OL,10,Fon environments and seems to miss out
OL,11,Fon the key factors contributing to
OL,12,Fharm, including normal birth ideology."
OL,14,FThe National Maternity and Neonatal
OL,15,FTaskforce, chaired by the Secretary of
OL,16,FState for Health and Social Care, will
OL,17,Fdevelop and oversee a new national
OL,18,Faction plan in response to Baroness
OL,19,FAmos's findings.
OL,26,@tD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G19/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
