PN,38220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FBaroness Amos said: "This report sets
OL,7,Fout practical action to change that.
OL,8,FIt recommends stronger national
OL,9,Fleadership, clearer accountability,
OL,10,Fbetter listening, safer service
OL,11,Fdesign, improved investigations,
OL,12,Fstronger team working and leadership,
OL,13,Fand investment in the buildings and
OL,14,Fdigital systems where families receive
OL,15,Fcare and deliver it.
OL,17,F"These recommendations must be
OL,18,Fimplemented in full. They are designed
OL,19,Fto deliver lasting system change,
OL,20,Fstrengthen accountability, and create
OL,21,Fa system that learns when harm occurs."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G20/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
