OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,FIn response to Amos's findings, Oxford
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals Trust said:
OL,9,F"We know that families' trust and
OL,10,Fconfidence in our maternity services
OL,11,Fhave been badly damaged. We also know
OL,12,Fthey will not be rebuilt by words
OL,13,Falone, and that what matters now is
OL,14,Fwhat we do next.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G21/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38222
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,F"We will place the experiences shared
OL,7,Fwith Baroness Amos and her team at the
OL,8,Fheart of our improvement plans. Women,
OL,9,Ffamilies and staff will be directly
OL,10,Finvolved in informing, shaping and
OL,11,Fdelivering the changes we make. We
OL,12,Fwill listen, act honestly, and be open
OL,13,Fabout the progress we are making and
OL,14,Fthe progress we still have to make.
OL,16,F"Our most recent CQC inspection
OL,17,Frecognised that change has begun, but
OL,18,Fthe experiences in this report show
OL,19,Fhow far we still have to travel, and
OL,20,Fwe do not underestimate that distance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G22/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38223
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,F"We will listen harder, act faster,
OL,7,Fand hold ourselves accountable for the
OL,8,Fimprovements that women, babies,
OL,9,Ffamilies and staff have every right to
OL,10,Fexpect.
OL,12,F"We will respond to both the national
OL,13,Freport and our own local report in
OL,14,Ffull, and we will act on them with
OL,15,Furgency. We will say clearly what we
OL,16,Fare changing, by when, and how women
OL,17,Fand families will see the difference.
OL,18,FAnd we will keep saying it, openly and
OL,19,Fhonestly, until trust in our services
OL,20,Fis rebuilt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G23/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38224
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782812888
OL,3,CMaternity review under fire as
OL,4,Cfamilies say "voices being written out"
OL,6,F"To every woman, baby and family we
OL,7,Ffailed, we are sorry. We have heard
OL,8,Fyou, and we are determined to be the
OL,9,Fservice you deserve."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G24/24
